## Development

### Installation

```bash
poetry install --with dev
```

### Running

```bash
poetry run git-analytics
```

### Tests

```bash
poetry run pytest
poetry run pytest --cov=git_analytics --cov-report=term-missing --cov-fail-under=45
```

### Type Checking

```bash
poetry run mypy .
```

### Linting

```bash
poetry run ruff check .
poetry run ruff check --select I .
```

